==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Middle voice of an apparently primary verb

===Pronunciation===
μάχομαι / machomai / makh'-om-ahee

===Verb===
'''μάχομαι'''

# to war, that is, (figuratively) to quarrel, dispute: - [[fight]], [[strive]].

